ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectContributions to assist livestock producers in Manitoba
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for FEDERAL CONTRIBUTIONS OF UP TO $3,000,000 TO ASSIST LIVESTOCK PRODUCERS in MANITOBA who are faced with significant forage shortfalls due to excess moisture and flooding conditions throughout the 2014 growing season.
